{"tid":2293993,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友讚佢公司秘書靚搞到我成晚都瞓唔著","createTime":"2020-11-20T16:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T01:02:22.000Z","uid":431,"like":15,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a6a3874eaf6832a3a5394de5ac5cf56327ac5e54","tid":2293993,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T16:05:39.000Z","msg":"我男朋友好少讚女仔靚..每次佢轉新公司..我都循例問佢有無靚女..佢次次都答無..今次我同樣地問佢..佢答&quot;無乜&quot;..咁即係有啦!!!!<br />\n<br />\n追問下原來佢覺得公司秘書靚..仲話係ceo福利..即係好似好羨慕個ceo咁款..之後我問佢個秘書係咪著低胸短裙高爭鞋..佢死都唔肯答..明知我嬲都唔答..佢話佢地唔會有交流..我問咁即係有交流就會中意佢啦..佢又叫我唔好亂諗..即係無否認啦<br />\n<br />\n我估個秘書係低胸短裙長腿..佢之前一句話中意小肥有身材嘅女仔..我就即刻增肥..但老實講..小肥嘅女仔著3無咁好睇..我而家決定減返肥...應該減幾磅就ok..之後著低胸短裙..出街比人望當報復!!睇佢以後仲敢唔敢讚人!!!"},{"pid":"de7b572d487b61d6f0c2a7ed0d3fa59eff83cef8","tid":2293993,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T16:06:15.000Z","msg":"google heychristy"},{"pid":"16fc243cfde1640b4294cd22349e0eb2817b39af","tid":2293993,"uid":104138,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T16:06:26.000Z","msg":"你都痴 9 線"},{"pid":"786f93bc11a0954f76c5cfe0aa16762a00f5e880","tid":2293993,"uid":227851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"又發咩癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603d810a5cdd65c61692a4e4cb004fc19c5b82d9","tid":2293993,"uid":371092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"又係你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d57d1af9fb0cd0763c26cb5c9321dbc4744361","tid":2293993,"uid":383914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T16:08:39.000Z","msg":"樓豬你個名意思掉轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0912c4a55b5292e27e8fe85fb4d0030066928366","tid":2293993,"uid":267395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T16:08:57